name: MPS Wireframe Toolkit 0.5.5 (Updated & Free)
description:
The MPS Wireframe Toolkit is a complete professional collection of low-fi elements and a system to create rapidly consistent wireframes. 


Over 50 low-fi elements you can use for the UX for a website, webshop or app.


To get an idea how it's looks and works see this video: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=R8mBxqXwk5o


The project got the following sections:


  1. Elements
  2. Blocks
  3. Partials
  4. Templates
  5. Structurals
  6. Publications


More info about the MPS approach: http://web.mps.systems
